{
  "comment": "Решение:\n\\( \\cfrac{-14}{(x-5)^2-2} \\geqslant 0 \\)\n\\( \\Rightarrow (x-5)^2-2<0\\), так как \\( -14<0 \\) и \\( \\cfrac{-14}{(x-5)^2-2} \\geqslant 0 \\)\n\\( (x-5)^2-2<0 \\)\n\\( (x-5)^2-(\\sqrt{2})^2<0 \\)\n\\( (x-5-\\sqrt{2})(x-5+\\sqrt{2})<0 \\)\n\\( (x-5-\\sqrt{2})(x-5+\\sqrt{2})=0 \\)\n\\( x-5-\\sqrt{2}=0 \\) или \\( x-5+\\sqrt{2}=0 \\)\n\\( x=5+\\sqrt{2 } \\) или \\( x=5-\\sqrt{2} \\)\nОтвет: \\( x \\in (5-\\sqrt{2};5+\\sqrt{2}) \\)",
